                  <provenance resp="#DLM">Written by frater <persName key="person_4342" role="scr">Johannes Molmecher</persName>: inscription, fol. 50v-51r. A Fr. Johannes Mulnmecher (d. 1479) was for thirty-six years confessor of the Convent of Poor Clares at Klarenthal, near Wiesbaden, in the diocese of Mainz (see <bibl>F. Otto, <title>Das Necrol. des Klosters Clarenthal bei Wiesbaden</title> (Veroffentlichen der hist. Comm. für Nassau III), 1901, p. 57</bibl>).</provenance>
